<div type="definition">
<p>TOOL USED FOR MEASURING TIME.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. The current general word for a sundial is biǎo 表.</p>
<p>2. Niè 臬 and guǐ 晷 are technical terms for a sundial.</p>
